
Medlars collection (1033 medical abstracts)

Data set link available in ``datasets```section of documentation. It is available at: http://web.eecs.utk.edu/research/lsi/. Download compressed version of document text. Extract the document, its 
name should be ``med.all``.

Directory structure should look like:

datasets/
  Medlars/
    med.all

In order to run the experiments, the user must only install the Medlars dataset in the proper directory. 